Package eu.iv4xr.ux.pxtesting.ltl

Class PXQueryEDSL

java.lang.Object
eu.iv4xr.ux.pxtesting.ltl.PXQueryEDSL
public class PXQueryEDSL extends Object
Extending Aplib's LTL DSL, see LTL, with more constructs to query/evaluate traces. Some constructs require enriched trace; see XStateTrace.
